Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Our tech-savvy E-GO Collection of bags lets you safely carry all your "tech-accessories" and look terrific doing it! You will find this bag essential to your lifestyle and your wardrobe and that it is the perfect bag for every day. Constructed from top quality, weather-resistant, all leather construction this bag is designed with strategic protection for your electronic essentials. Padded compartments are designed for laptop, tablet, reader or similar devices and interior compartments to protect smart phone and music player give ample space. A top zipper closure to secure electronics and personal belongings also makes for easy access. A inside zipper pocket is the perfect place for passport and personal items. The convenient rear slip-thru pocket lets you trolley with rolling bag. Additional items like a key keeper and convenient ID tag, protective cloth storage bag and comfortable handles with 9.5-Inch drop make this bag the perfect choice for all of your equipment. What fits inside: Up to 15-Inch laptop computer and a protective insert for DSLR and 1-2 moderately sized lenses. Or many combinations of smaller items including laptop, reader and compact camera plus notebook, water bottle, umbrella, flip-flops, healthy snacks and wallet, keys, make-up, hair brush, hand sanitizer, tin of mints all your lifestyle essentials.
